{
  "video_id": "Dh5sPiuaO9Y",
  "title": "Hunting for Peru's lost civilizations -- with satellites | Sarah Parcak",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13440.0,
      "end_time": 16160.0,
      "text": "In July of 1911,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16160.0,
      "end_time": 21440.0,
      "text": "a 35-year-old Yale graduate and professor set out from his rainforest camp"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21440.0,
      "end_time": 23080.0,
      "text": "with his team."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23080.0,
      "end_time": 25240.0,
      "text": "After climbing a steep hill"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25240.0,
      "end_time": 27680.0,
      "text": "and wiping the sweat from his brow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27680.0,
      "end_time": 31000.0,
      "text": "he described what he saw beneath him."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31000.0,
      "end_time": 34200.0,
      "text": "He saw rising from the dense rainforest foliage"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34200.0,
      "end_time": 37800.0,
      "text": "this incredible interlocking maze of structures"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 37800.0,
      "end_time": 39120.0,
      "text": "built of granite,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39120.0,
      "end_time": 41360.0,
      "text": "beautifully put together."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41360.0,
      "end_time": 43000.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s amazing about this project"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 43000.0,
      "end_time": 46000.0,
      "text": "is that it was the first funded by National Geographic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 46000.0,
      "end_time": 50640.0,
      "text": "and it graced the front cover of its magazine in 1912."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 50640.0,
      "end_time": 54800.0,
      "text": "This professor used state-of-the-art photography equipment"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 54800.0,
      "end_time": 56480.0,
      "text": "to record the site,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 56480.0,
      "end_time": 60000.0,
      "text": "forever changing the face of exploration."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 60000.0,
      "end_time": 62960.0,
      "text": "The site was Machu Picchu,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 62960.0,
      "end_time": 67320.0,
      "text": "discovered and explored by Hiram Bingham."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 67320.0,
      "end_time": 69280.0,
      "text": "When he saw the site, he asked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 69280.0,
      "end_time": 71840.0,
      "text": "&quot;This is an impossible dream."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 71840.0,
      "end_time": 74360.0,
      "text": "What could it be?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 74360.0,
      "end_time": 76720.0,
      "text": "So today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 76720.0,
      "end_time": 79280.0,
      "text": "100 years later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 79280.0,
      "end_time": 83520.0,
      "text": "I invite you all on an incredible journey with me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 83520.0,
      "end_time": 86440.0,
      "text": "a 37-year-old Yale graduate and professor."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 86440.0,
      "end_time": 88600.0,
      "text": "(Cheers)"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 88600.0,
      "end_time": 92040.0,
      "text": "We will do nothing less than use state-of-the-art technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 92040.0,
      "end_time": 95760.0,
      "text": "to map an entire country."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 95760.0,
      "end_time": 98720.0,
      "text": "This is a dream started by Hiram Bingham,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 98720.0,
      "end_time": 102160.0,
      "text": "but we are expanding it to the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 102160.0,
      "end_time": 107320.0,
      "text": "making archaeological exploration more open, inclusive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 107320.0,
      "end_time": 111200.0,
      "text": "and at a scale simply not previously possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 111200.0,
      "end_time": 114040.0,
      "text": "This is why I am so excited"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 114040.0,
      "end_time": 116160.0,
      "text": "to share with you all today"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 116160.0,
      "end_time": 121440.0,
      "text": "that we will begin the 2016 TED Prize platform"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 121440.0,
      "end_time": 123640.0,
      "text": "in Latin America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 123640.0,
      "end_time": 127040.0,
      "text": "more specifically Peru."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 127040.0,
      "end_time": 128280.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 128280.0,
      "end_time": 133880.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 133880.0,
      "end_time": 137520.0,
      "text": "We will be taking Hiram Bingham&#39;s impossible dream"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 137520.0,
      "end_time": 140759.0,
      "text": "and turning it into an amazing future"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 140759.0,
      "end_time": 143640.0,
      "text": "that we can all share in together."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 143640.0,
      "end_time": 145560.0,
      "text": "So Peru doesn&#39;t just have Machu Picchu."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 145560.0,
      "end_time": 148560.0,
      "text": "It has absolutely stunning jewelry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 148560.0,
      "end_time": 150400.0,
      "text": "like what you can see here."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 150400.0,
      "end_time": 154440.0,
      "text": "It has amazing Moche pottery of human figures."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 154440.0,
      "end_time": 156280.0,
      "text": "It has the Nazca Lines"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 156280.0,
      "end_time": 158800.0,
      "text": "and amazing textiles."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 158800.0,
      "end_time": 161680.0,
      "text": "So as part of the TED Prize platform,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 161680.0,
      "end_time": 164760.0,
      "text": "we are going to partnering with some incredible organizations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 164760.0,
      "end_time": 168240.0,
      "text": "first of all with DigitalGlobe, the world&#39;s largest provider"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 168240.0,
      "end_time": 171360.0,
      "text": "of high-resolution commercial satellite imagery."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 171360.0,
      "end_time": 173880.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re going to be helping us build out"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 173880.0,
      "end_time": 176080.0,
      "text": "this amazing crowdsourcing platform they have."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 176080.0,
      "end_time": 177400.0,
      "text": "Maybe some of you used it"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 177400.0,
      "end_time": 181680.0,
      "text": "with the MH370 crash and search for the airplane."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 181680.0,
      "end_time": 184880.0,
      "text": "Of course, they&#39;ll also be providing us with the satellite imagery."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 184880.0,
      "end_time": 188720.0,
      "text": "National Geographic will be helping us with education and of course exploration."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 188720.0,
      "end_time": 192160.0,
      "text": "As well, they&#39;ll be providing us with rich content for the platform,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 192160.0,
      "end_time": 196160.0,
      "text": "including some of the archival imagery like you saw at the beginning of this talk"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 196160.0,
      "end_time": 199720.0,
      "text": "and some of their documentary footage."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 199720.0,
      "end_time": 202160.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve already begun to build and plan the platform,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 202160.0,
      "end_time": 204440.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m just so excited."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 204440.0,
      "end_time": 205920.0,
      "text": "So here&#39;s the cool part."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 205920.0,
      "end_time": 208520.0,
      "text": "My team, headed up by Chase Childs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 208520.0,
      "end_time": 211960.0,
      "text": "is already beginning to look at some of the satellite imagery."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 211960.0,
      "end_time": 215200.0,
      "text": "Of course, what you can see here is 0.3-meter data."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 215200.0,
      "end_time": 217440.0,
      "text": "This is site called Chan Chan in northern Peru."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 217440.0,
      "end_time": 219440.0,
      "text": "It dates to 850 AD."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 219440.0,
      "end_time": 221840.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a really amazing city, but let&#39;s zoom in."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 221840.0,
      "end_time": 226240.0,
      "text": "This is the type and quality of data that you all will get to see."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 226240.0,
      "end_time": 229280.0,
      "text": "You can see individual structures, individual buildings."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 229280.0,
      "end_time": 232680.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;ve already begun to find previously unknown sites."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 232680.0,
      "end_time": 235360.0,
      "text": "What we can say already is that as part of the platform,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 235360.0,
      "end_time": 239000.0,
      "text": "you will all help discover thousands of previously unknown sites,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 239000.0,
      "end_time": 240520.0,
      "text": "like this one here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 240520.0,
      "end_time": 242840.0,
      "text": "and this potentially large one here."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 242840.0,
      "end_time": 247320.0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, we&#39;ve also begun to uncover large-scale looting at sites,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 247320.0,
      "end_time": 248600.0,
      "text": "like what you see here."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 248600.0,
      "end_time": 250640.0,
      "text": "So many sites in Peru are threatened,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 250640.0,
      "end_time": 252720.0,
      "text": "but the great part is that all of this data"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 252720.0,
      "end_time": 255760.0,
      "text": "is going to be shared with archaeologists on the front lines"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 255760.0,
      "end_time": 258280.0,
      "text": "of protecting these sites."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 258279.99999999997,
      "end_time": 261719.99999999997,
      "text": "So I was just in Peru, meeting with their Minister of Culture"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 261720.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263000.0,
      "text": "as well as UNESCO."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 263000.0,
      "end_time": 265200.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ll be collaborating closely with them."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 265200.0,
      "end_time": 266480.0,
      "text": "Just so you all know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 266480.0,
      "end_time": 269240.0,
      "text": "the site is going to be in both English and Spanish,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 269240.0,
      "end_time": 271279.0,
      "text": "which is absolutely essential to make sure"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 271279.0,
      "end_time": 275240.0,
      "text": "that people in Peru and across Latin America can participate."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 275240.0,
      "end_time": 279320.0,
      "text": "Our main project coprincipal investigator is the gentleman you see here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 279320.0,
      "end_time": 281400.0,
      "text": "Dr. Luis Jaime Castillo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 281400.0,
      "end_time": 283720.0,
      "text": "professor at Catholic University."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 283720.0,
      "end_time": 287760.0,
      "text": "As a respected Peruvian archaeologist and former vice-minister,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 287760.0,
      "end_time": 291920.0,
      "text": "Dr. Castillo will be helping us coordinate and share the data with archaeologists"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 291920.0,
      "end_time": 294280.0,
      "text": "so they can explore these sites on the ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 294280.0,
      "end_time": 297680.0,
      "text": "He also runs this amazing drone mapping program,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 297680.0,
      "end_time": 300760.0,
      "text": "some of the images of which you can see behind me here and here."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 300760.0,
      "end_time": 303600.0,
      "text": "And this data will be incorporated into the platform,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 303600.0,
      "end_time": 308240.0,
      "text": "and also he&#39;ll be helping to image some of the new sites you help find."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 308240.0,
      "end_time": 310400.0,
      "text": "Our on-the-ground partner"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 310400.0,
      "end_time": 313600.0,
      "text": "who will be helping us with education, outreach,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 313600.0,
      "end_time": 315529.0,
      "text": "as well as site preservation components,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 315529.0,
      "end_time": 317553.0,
      "text": "is the Sustainable Preservation Initiative,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 317553.0,
      "end_time": 319320.0,
      "text": "led by Dr. Larry Coben."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 319320.0,
      "end_time": 320720.0,
      "text": "Some of you may not be aware"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 320720.0,
      "end_time": 322840.0,
      "text": "that some of the world&#39;s poorest communities"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 322840.0,
      "end_time": 326680.0,
      "text": "coexist with some of the world&#39;s most well-known archaeological sites."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 326680.0,
      "end_time": 328160.0,
      "text": "What SPI does"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 328160.0,
      "end_time": 330160.0,
      "text": "is it helps to empower these communities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 330160.0,
      "end_time": 331960.0,
      "text": "in particular women,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 331960.0,
      "end_time": 335080.0,
      "text": "with new economic approaches and business training."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 335080.0,
      "end_time": 338520.0,
      "text": "So it helps to teach them to create beautiful handicrafts"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 338520.0,
      "end_time": 340520.0,
      "text": "which are then sold on to tourists."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 340520.0,
      "end_time": 344720.0,
      "text": "This empowers the women to treasure their cultural heritage"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 344720.0,
      "end_time": 346400.0,
      "text": "and take ownership of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 346400.0,
      "end_time": 350360.0,
      "text": "I had the opportunity to spend some time with 24 of these women"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 350360.0,
      "end_time": 355000.0,
      "text": "at a well-known archaeological site called Pachacamac, just outside Lima."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 355000.0,
      "end_time": 357440.0,
      "text": "These women were unbelievably inspiring,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 357440.0,
      "end_time": 361600.0,
      "text": "and what&#39;s great is that SPI will help us transform communities"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 361600.0,
      "end_time": 364800.0,
      "text": "near some of the sites that you help to discover."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 364800.0,
      "end_time": 366960.0,
      "text": "Peru is just the beginning."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 366960.0,
      "end_time": 369600.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re going to be expanding this platform to the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 369600.0,
      "end_time": 371840.0,
      "text": "but already I&#39;ve gotten thousands of emails"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 371840.0,
      "end_time": 375520.0,
      "text": "from people all across the world -- professors, educators, students,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 375520.0,
      "end_time": 379080.0,
      "text": "and other archaeologists -- who are so excited to help participate."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 379080.0,
      "end_time": 383720.0,
      "text": "In fact, they&#39;re already suggesting amazing places for us to help discover,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 383720.0,
      "end_time": 385600.0,
      "text": "including Atlantis."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 385600.0,
      "end_time": 388240.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t know if we&#39;re going to be looking for Atlantis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 388240.0,
      "end_time": 389480.0,
      "text": "but you never know."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 389480.0,
      "end_time": 392600.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m just so excited to launch this platform."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 392600.0,
      "end_time": 395400.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s going to be launched formally by the end of the year."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 395400.0,
      "end_time": 396760.0,
      "text": "And I have to say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 396760.0,
      "end_time": 402640.0,
      "text": "if what my team has already discovered in the past few weeks are any indication,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 402640.0,
      "end_time": 407080.0,
